    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="2SA 23:38"/>Ira, de Jéther.</para>
  <para style="q" vid="2SA 23:38">Gareb, de Jéther.<verse eid="2SA 23:38"/></para>
  <para style="q">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="2SA 23:39"/>Urie, le Héthien.</para>
  <para style="q" vid="2SA 23:39">En tout, trente-sept.<verse eid="2SA 23:39"/></para>
